[Name] BashBurn
[Summary] Sick of all those fancy CD-burning apps not working for you? You need something that just gets the work done? Welcome to BashBurn - It just works! 
[License] GNU GPL Version 2
[Description] BashBurn is the new name for the cd burning shell script Magma. It's not the best looking CD-burning application out there, but it does what you want it to do. (And if not then probably didn't want to do it anyway)
[Homepage] https://bashburn.sourceforge.net/
